HEADWORD: Indebtedness
<hw>In*debt"ed*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state of
being indebted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The sum owed; debts, collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indebtment</ent>⟦br⟧
